2.2 Visualization

What five players have the most goals scored against?

library(dplyr)
top_5_goalies <- Goalies %>%
  arrange(desc(PostGA)) %>%
  head(5)

specific_goalies1 <- c("hrudeke01", "bannemu01", "daleyjo01", "hextaro01", 
                       "fleurma01")
top_5_data <- subset(Goalies, playerID %in% specific_goalies1)


ggplot(top_5_data, aes(x = playerID, fill = PostGA)) +
  geom_bar()

The player with playerID ‚Äúbannemu01‚Äù showed the highest number of goals scored against

What is the relationship between goalie shutouts and wins?

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data = Goalies) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = SHO, y = W))

There is a positive relationship between goalie shutouts and wins. So, if a goalie continues tp have shutouts, the teams chances of wining increase signifitcantly
